commit.message:
Updated README

Included Awards and some Instructions
Changed baseurl to reflect project restructuring

Restructured project

Assets were moved to a directory within the project root titled
`assets`.

Audio files are in a subdirectory titled `audio` which
contains two subdirectories itself, `final` and `split`. Final
is the final audio to be used within the game.  Split contains
individual tracks with lines from the voice actors.

Assets targeting print are within a subdirectory of `assets`
titled `print`.  These include the booklet and the board.

Removed auto-created backup files

These were never meant to be part of the repo, it's easy to mess
up and add all when it's the early morning and you haven't slept
:-)
added things that need to be printed
json should be fully fleshed out

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/nickgirardo/dreamphone

Reincorporating changes from upstream
